{"tid":2179970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想代全民檢測澄清一件事","createTime":"2020-08-29T13:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:36:49.000Z","uid":78793,"like":12,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c39a64cb60074934533a9d40a86c53d4e82d5a10","tid":2179970,"uid":78793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"大家一直流傳將支棒插入鼻腔20 cm係嚴重錯誤<br />\n其實檢測過程只做兩件事<br />\n<br />\n第一，將支測試棒插入鼻孔2cm左右，即係尾指第一節左右咁長，平時撩鼻屎嘅深度<br />\n<br />\n第二，攞另一支測試棒插入口腔，去撩個扁桃腺位同埋吊鐘後面嘅喉嚨（注意⚠️係唔會掂到吊鐘）<br />\n<br />\n大家所講嘅DNA陰謀論我個人就唔加以評論，只係想幫手澄清番個正確檢驗程序<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好好似內容農場咁，胡亂散播又錯又假嘅消息<br />\n<br />\n利申：已做Training"},{"pid":"dc9716a89f9ea4033d392dde547c9a54d4eeee88","tid":2179970,"uid":22755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"撩得唔夠入都唔準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1fb88a066679d03a825271aec821dc7fe9f75b","tid":2179970,"uid":274129,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc9716a89f9ea4033d392dde547c9a54d4eeee88","tid":2179970,"uid":22755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"撩得唔夠入都唔準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:36:04.000Z","msg":"吊鐘後面都唔夠入？撩埋入個肺好冇？"},{"pid":"0de7adbb1c0027f1f8b6c72d9a3e56501f242c80","tid":2179970,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:36:13.000Z","msg":"撩得咁淺，同lur口水有咩分別"},{"pid":"b986bc75a3c8970b868e3e6eff1ac9cc49e5ecd9","tid":2179970,"uid":78793,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ab1fb88a066679d03a825271aec821dc7fe9f75b","tid":2179970,"uid":274129,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc9716a89f9ea4033d392dde547c9a54d4eeee88","tid":2179970,"uid":22755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"撩得唔夠入都唔準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim